summary: 'It Can Be Exhausting Trying To Make It In LA': What's Next For Jodie Comer - The Liverpudlian Who Has Hollywood Firmly At Her...
title: 'It Can Be Exhausting Trying To Make It In LA': What's Next For Jodie Comer - The Liverpudlian Who Has Hollywood Firmly At Her Feet?
excerpt: Jodie Comer won our hearts as Villanelle in Killing Eve. She also has Doctor Foster and Thirteen on her CV, but what's next for the Liverpudlian actress?
description: Don’t expect any of this to change her, though. Jodie has said that she doesn’t want to get ‘caught up’ in being obsessed with her social media presence or going to constant events. ‘Your popularity and social media following can be a reason you get a role, so actors can get caught up in it,’ she said on the Two Shot Podcast in December. ‘Actors and actresses attend more events than I see them on screen. at’s something I definitely don’t want to do.’
